CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 10, 1957, pg. 17, reads: "Slums Growing in Homewood? - Scrap Yard? - These two apparently abandoned trucks and the pile of old lumber, shown on the right, form an ugly picture on Tioga St., where they are located. - Harris Photo"
TitMainTitle: Vacant overgrown lot with two trucks and pile of lumber, Tioga Street, Homewood
